  "text": "The meta-analysis of five studies resulted in a pooled relative risk of 0.54 [0.41, 0.71] (Fig. 7) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . The I value was 43 %. The quality of evidence was rated as moderate (Table 1) . Of note, one of the included studies reported data based on a time-series analysis, but we opted to analyze it as a before and after study in order to include it in the meta-analysis. The sensitivity analysis excluding the one study that did not report separately data for devices for intramuscular, subcutaneous or intradermal injection devices [CITATION_6] ",
